<tr class="odd"><td><a href="mod_authn_dbd.html#authdbduserrealmquery">AuthDBDUserRealmQuery <var>requ&ecirc;te</var></a></td><td></td><td>d</td><td>E</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td class="descr" colspan="4">Requ&ecirc;te SQL servant &agrave; v&eacute;rifier une empreinte de mot de
