<tr><td><a href="mod_vhost_alias.html#virtualscriptaliasip">VirtualScriptAliasIP <em>r&eacute;pertoire-interpol&eacute;</em>|none</a></td><td> none </td><td>sv</td><td>E</td></tr><tr><td class="descr" colspan="4">Configuration dynamique du r&eacute;pertoire des scripts CGI pour
un serveur virtuel donn&eacute;</td></tr>
<tr class="odd"><td><a href="mod_watchdog.html#watchdoginterval" id="W" name="W">WatchdogInterval <var>time-interval</var>[s]</a></td><td> 1 </td><td>s</td><td>B</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td class="descr" colspan="4">Intervalle Watchdog en secondes</td></tr>
<tr><td><a href="mod_include.html#xbithack" id="X" name="X">XBitHack on|off|full</a></td><td> off </td><td>svdh</td><td>B</td></tr><tr><td class="descr" colspan="4">Interpr&egrave;te les directives SSI dans les fichiers dont le bit
